---
title: Asian-Style Sichuan Pork with Garlic Rice
description: When this dish was brought to our test kitchen table, it disappeared in record time! With a delicious combination of snow peas, Asian greens, toasted sesame seeds and pork with mild Sichuan garlic paste, it's sure to be a hit at your table too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d9e619acf275630fa5d2e52-fd7bfb3c.jpg
